---

import Header from '../../components/Header'
import Footer from '../../components/Footer'
import RequestQuoteForm from '../../components/RequestQuoteForm'
import whitePhone from '../../assets/white-phone.svg'
import yardSign from '../../assets/yard-sign-Opt.jpg'
import love from '../../assets/love.svg'

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" href="../../AlderFavicon.png" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
        <meta name="description" content="Looking for home security New York City? At Alder, we can give you some of the best customer service to help set up your new system. " />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Home Security Systems New York City | Alder Home Security</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-white w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center">

        <Header path='/states/new-york' client:load />

        <br/>

        <div class="w-full h-[325px] bg-cover bg-center max-w-6xl" style={{
            backgroundImage: 'url("https://res.cloudinary.com/alder/image/upload/q_auto,f_auto/v1565632234/NewYork.jpg")'
        }}>
        <div class="w-full h-full flex flex-col items-center gap-8 justify-center bg-neutral-800/[.50]">

            <h1 class="text-white font-medium w-4/5 md:w-1/2 text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl text-center">Home Security New York City</h1>

            <a href="tel:800-710-1289" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:scale-105 transition duration-100 py-2 px-4 rounded-3xl border-2 z-10 border-white">
                <img alt="phone icon" src={whitePhone}/>
                <p class="text-white text-[15px]">Call Now 800-710-1289</p>
            </a>
            
        </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full max-w-6xl py-20 px-4 bg-white flex justify-center items-center ">

            <p class="text-[#58585B] leading-7 w-full md:w-4/5 lg:w-2/3 text-center">New York City is known for being one of the largest cities in the United States. Its bustling streets, excited atmosphere, and great personality make it one of the most visited destinations. There is so much to do and see in New York City that it can sometimes be overwhelming. With so many people coming and going from New York City and so many people trying to “make it” in the big city, those who live in the city often worry about home security. To fix the worry, residents should look to find home security systems that fit into their lifestyle and budget. Here’s what you should be looking for.</p>

        </div>

        <RequestQuoteForm client:load bg_color="bg-[#61798F]" />

        <br/>
        <br/>

        <div class="w-full max-w-6xl bg-cover" style={{
            backgroundImage: 'url("https://res.cloudinary.com/alder/image/upload/q_auto,f_auto/v1557271904/Map_Screen_Shot.png")'
        }} >
        <div class="w-full h-full bg-[#297CA3]/[.50] flex flex-col items-center py-4 px-6 gap-4 justify-evenly">
                <h2 class="flex flex-row items-center text-2xl sm:text-6xl text-white font-medium gap-2 bg-neutral-800/[.75] p-2 rounded-xl ">WE <img alt="heart" class=" w-[30px] h-[30px] sm:w-[65px] sm:h-[65px]" src={love}/> NEW YORK </h2>

                <p class="text-white bg-neutral-800/[.85] text-sm md:text-base w-full md:w-2/3 p-4 leading-6 ">There is a reason why people from New York love Alder Home Security. We do some of our best work in New York and the people love us because of it. Our home security systems are easy to set up (they are DIY), and they are one of the most efficient systems on the market. We want to ensure that you feel that you can trust us on all levels with the protection and safety of your home and family. Because of that, we make sure that put your family in mind with every system that we send out. When we walk you through setting up a home security system, we act as if it is our own family who is getting the home security system. We put care into ensuring that everything is working correctly and we leave no room for mistakes. With Alder Home Security, you can be sure that you have home protection at every hour of the day or night.</p>
        </div>
        </div>

        <br/>
        <br/>

        <div class="w-full max-w-4xl bg-cover bg-center " style={{
            backgroundImage: `url(${yardSign})`
        }} >
        <div class="w-full h-full bg-neutral-800/[.75] md:bg-neutral-800/[.45] flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 py-8 px-4 md:px-12">

            <h3 class="text-white text-2xl">Look For a Security System</h3>

            <h3 class="text-white text-4xl font-medium">in the Budget</h3>

            <p class="text-white text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium md:w-1/2 leading-6">The first thing you should always keep in mind is your budget. You never want to get a security system that pushes your outside of your budget and makes you have to cut other important things out of your life. Home security is important. However, it also important to ensure that you are financially stable. Luckily, there are home security systems for every group of people. There are security systems that cost thousands of dollars a year and there are others that cost only a couple hundred dollars a year. Find the one that fits you. The main difference in the price of home security systems is the type of system. If you get a full security system that is monitored and set up by professionals, the security system will cost more. However, if you’re looking for a DIY security system, it will cost you a lot less overall. You should also only get the features that you need if you’re struggling to fit the basic security system in your budget. Security cameras are one of the most important features, so as long as you have those set up, you should be good to go.</p>

        </div>
        </div>

        <br/>
        <br/>

        <div class="w-full max-w-6xl flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-full h-[250px] bg-cover" style={{
                backgroundImage: 'url("https://res.cloudinary.com/alder/image/upload/v1557333574/simple.jpg")',
                backgroundPosition: "center 85%"
            }} />

            <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 md:gap-0 md:flex-row px-4 py-12 ">

                <div class=" w-full md:w-[25%] flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-4">
                    <h3 class="text-[#58585B] font-medium text-2xl text-center md:text-left ">Setting Up Alarm Security</h3>
                </div>

                <p class="text-[#58585B] text-sm leading-6 w-full md:w-[65%] " >
                    When you set up an alarm system, you will be setting up the protection for your home and family. To do this best, you should know more about the system that you will be installing. Here at Alder, we offer the best DIY alarm system on the market. It’s easy to set up and we give you some easy-to-follow instructions along with the alarm system. Once you have the alarm system armed and ready to go, you can start placing other things around the home. Put window sensors on the windows and door sensors on every door that leads into the home. This ensures that if anyone opens a door or window while the security system is armed, you will be immediately alerted. You should also set up the Alder app on your phone to be able to look through your security cameras around the home. The app will also send you push notifications if an alarm is triggered.
                </p>

            </div>

        </div>
        
    
        <Footer />

    </body>
</html>